<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Configure colors in CSS files</b></p><p>IntelliJ IDEA makes it easy to specify colors in CSS files. The <span class="code_emphasis">color</span> properties have icons of the corresponding color in the editor gutter. Click the icon to choose the desired color using the color picker.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ps_tips-cssColor.png" alt="CSS color" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>